This license does not apply to games/applications made with the software, only the software itself
as well as any derivative works of it. If you change the source code of Love Game Maker itself, it
falls under this license. If you instead simply use it to create a game, that game is yours and may
be licensed as you please.

If you have any questions regarding the usage of this application not answered by this license, please
contact the developer of the application at radfordhound@gmail.com. Thank you for using Love Game Maker.